---
<section class="relative h-[90vh] w-full flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-gray-900">
  
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 overflow-hidden">
    <iframe
      class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 w-[177.77vh] min-w-full min-h-[56.25vw] h-full -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 pointer-events-none opacity-60"
      src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9A2FomgdHSE?autoplay=1&mute=1&controls=0&disablekb=1&fs=0&loop=1&playlist=9A2FomgdHSE&start=8&end=47&showinfo=0&rel=0&iv_load_policy=3&modestbranding=1"
      title="Hero Video Background"
      frameborder="0"
      allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
    ></iframe>
    
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900/90 via-gray-900/60 to-gray-900/30"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    
    <div class="text-white space-y-6">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight">
        Seguridad <br/>
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-omerhsa-primary to-blue-300">Inteligente</span> <br/>
        para tu vida.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-200 max-w-lg leading-relaxed shadow-sm">
        Gestiona riesgos y protege tu patrimonio con la solidez de OMERHSA. Más de 20 años blindando el futuro de las familias y empresas en Honduras.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-6 shadow-2xl lg:ml-auto max-w-md w-full border border-gray-100/20 backdrop-blur-sm">
      <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Cotiza tu Seguro</h3>
        <span class="bg-omerhsa-light text-omerhsa-primary text-xs font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Rápido</span>
      </div>

      <form action="/cotizar" class="space-y-4">
        <div>
          <label class="block text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase mb-1">Tipo de Protección</label>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
            <button type="button" class="px-4 py-3 rounded-xl bg-omerhsa-primary text-white text-sm font-medium shadow-md transition hover:scale-105">Vehículos</button>
            <button type="button" class="px-4 py-3 rounded-xl bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-200 transition">Incendio</button>
            <button type="button" class="px-4 py-3 rounded-xl bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-200 transition">Vida</button>
            <button type="button" class="px-4 py-3 rounded-xl bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-gray-200 transition">Gastos medicos</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <label class="block text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase mb-1">Tu Presupuesto (Aprox)</label>
          <input type="range" class="w-full accent-omerhsa-primary h-2 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg appearance-none cursor-pointer" />
          <div class="flex justify-between text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">
            <span>Básico</span>
            <span>Premium</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <button type="submit" class="w-full py-4 bg-gray-900 hover:bg-omerhsa-dark text-white rounded-xl font-bold text-lg transition-all shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-2 group">
          Iniciar Cotización
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path></svg>
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>